## Validation checklist (self-check before considering a page complete)

### File and directory
- [ ] Entry file is `index.html`; stylesheet is `style.css`; JS (if any) is `script.js`.
- [ ] No copied `zohocustom.css` or `product.css` inside the page directory — these must be linked from `../source/`.
- [ ] No scratch, temporary, or backup files (`Untitled-*`, `*.backup`, `test*.html`) in the directory.
- [ ] No `assets/` folder has been created or populated during development — placeholders are used for all images and SVGs.

### Images and placeholders
- [ ] Every `<img>` uses `https://prezohoweb.zoho.com/` — not `placehold.co`, local paths, or other CDN URLs.
- [ ] Every `<img>` placeholder has `width` and `height` matching the Figma design, and a descriptive `alt`.
- [ ] Every `<img>` placeholder is marked with `<!-- TODO: replace with final asset -->` in HTML.
- [ ] Every CSS banner/background placeholder uses `background-image: url('https://prezohoweb.zoho.com/')` with cover/center/no-repeat and a `/* TODO */` comment.
- [ ] Every UI control icon and icon sprite uses the same placeholder URL as `background-image` with a `/* TODO */` comment.
- [ ] No SVG files copied from other projects — inline grey-rectangle `<rect>` placeholders used instead.
- [ ] No `assets/` folder created or populated during development.
- [ ] CSS `linear-gradient` values are left untouched — they are design tokens, not asset references.

### Output and structure
- [ ] `.page-container` > `<section class="...">` > `.content-wrap` pattern used throughout.
- [ ] Heading hierarchy is correct (H1 → H2 → H3, no skips); one H1 per page.
- [ ] All classes are semantic and BEM-like; no inline styles in HTML.

### Markup
- [ ] No inline event handlers; all behaviour is in `script.js` or an inline `<script>` block at the bottom of `<body>`.

### CSS and typography
- [ ] Global typography and utilities block is at the top of `style.css`.
- [ ] All `h2` are `32px`; all `h3` across components are `20px` — no arbitrary overrides.
- [ ] All `p` and `li` have `font-size: 16px` and `line-height: 1.75` — not left unset.
- [ ] Card and panel padding is `24px` desktop — not a mix of values.
- [ ] Grid and flex `gap` is `20px` — not a mix of values.
- [ ] All six responsive breakpoints are present and follow the standard type scale.
- [ ] No `zohocustom.css` or `product.css` styles overridden without a design reason.

### Source of truth
- [ ] **Figma → Code:** Build matches the provided Figma at key breakpoints; no inventing layout or copy not in the design.
- [ ] **Content-docs / Revamp:** All copy and structure come from the reference docs; gaps are flagged before the page is considered complete.

